OL,3,C'It will be the end of him': Wife's
OL,4,Cfears for husband if forced into care
OL,6,FA County Tyrone woman fears "it will
OL,7,Fbe the end" of her husband if he is
OL,8,Fforced into a care home because there
OL,9,Fare not enough staff to provide him
OL,10,Fwith adequate care at his home.
OL,12,FMarian and Jim Teague have been
OL,13,Fhappily married for 21 years, but in
OL,14,F2015, Jim was diagnosed with
OL,15,FAlzheimer's.
OL,17,FThe 86-year-old has been in hospital
OL,18,Fsince Boxing Day but cannot be
OL,19,Fdischarged because the Western Trust
OL,20,Fdoes not have the staff to look after
OL,21,Fhim at home.
