OL,3,C'It will be the end of him': Wife's
OL,4,Cfears for husband if forced into care
OL,6,FThe home they share in Mountfield
OL,7,Foutside Omagh is already specially
OL,8,Fadapted and he has a hospital bed.
OL,10,FBut the Western Trust are unable to
OL,11,Ffind the staff.
OL,13,FIn a statement the Trust said:
OL,14,F"Discharge planning includes assessing
OL,15,Fa patient's needs and identifying the
OL,16,Fmeans to meet those needs.
