OL,6,F"This includes exploring support from
OL,7,Ffamily and other community support. We
OL,8,Fdiscuss all of these issues with
OL,9,Fpatients and their families to
OL,10,Fdetermine what may be available to
OL,11,Fthem, however we understand not all
OL,12,Ffamily or carers can provide care due
OL,13,Fto their own commitments or health
OL,14,Fissues."
