OL,3,C'It will be the end of him': Wife's
OL,4,Cfears for husband if forced into care
OL,6,F"Appropriate discharge also reduces
OL,7,Fthe risk of infection and frees up bed
OL,8,Fcapacity for very sick patients who
OL,9,Frequire acute hospital care."
OL,11,FThe statement continued: "When all
OL,12,Fpossible arrangements and options have
OL,13,Fbeen offered and declined by a family,
OL,14,Fthe patient may be discharged to
OL,15,Finterim care arrangements.
