OL,3,C'It will be the end of him': Wife's
OL,4,Cfears for husband if forced into care
OL,6,F"Temporary placement within an
OL,7,Fappropriate care facility will be
OL,8,Fsought as close to the patient's own
OL,9,Fhome, as far as is reasonably possible
OL,10,F` this is in keeping with all health
OL,11,Fand social care trusts."
OL,13,FJim has recently been transferred from
OL,14,FAltnagelvin in Londonderry to the
OL,15,FSouth West Acute Hospital in
OL,16,FEnniskillen.
