OL,3,C'It will be the end of him': Wife's
OL,4,Cfears for husband if forced into care
OL,6,F"It's hard to see him deteriorating in
OL,7,Fthe hospital bed," his wife added. "I
OL,8,Fcan see his muscles are gone. What
OL,9,Flittle he has. He is just laying
OL,10,Fthere. There's no interaction with him
OL,11,Fanymore.
OL,13,F"Whereas if he was in his chair he
OL,14,Fwould be complaining about the soaps I
OL,15,Fwas watching... and people would be
OL,16,Fcoming to see him".
